RESEARCH_MUNICIPALITY.notes: Davenport, Washington, operates under a mayor-council form of government. Brad Sweet was elected Mayor in the November 4, 2025, general election. Preliminary results from the same election indicate Michael Strite won Councilman Position No. 1, Lance Strite won Councilman Position No. 3, and Chris Stein won Councilman Position No. 4. The city council consists of five members, but the names for Council Member Position 2 and Position 5 could not be definitively identified from the available search results for Davenport, WA. Information regarding 'alderman' and 'wards' found in some search results pertains to Davenport, Iowa, not Davenport, Washington.
